'''沙丘鹤'''（[[学名|学名]]：{{lang|la|''Antigone canadensis''}}）为[[鹤科|鹤科]]赤颈鹤属的大型[[涉禽|涉禽]]。该物种的[[模式产地|模式产地]]在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[哈得逊湾|哈得逊湾]]。<ref name='id1792'/>其种名“{{lang|la|canadensis}}”为[[加拿大|加拿大]]的[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]形式。<ref name= job>{{cite book | last=Jobling | first= James A | year= 2010| title= The Helm Dictionary of Scientific Bird Names | url=https://archive.org/details/Helm_Dictionary_of_Scientific_Bird_Names_by_James_A._Jobling | publisher = Christopher Helm | location = [[London|London]] | isbn = 978-1-4081-2501-4 |pages =[https://archive.org/details/Helm_Dictionary_of_Scientific_Bird_Names_by_James_A._Jobling/page/n87 87]}}</ref>

==外形==
成年沙丘鹤外表为[[灰色|灰色]]；在繁殖期，特別是在[[遷徙|遷徙]]的亚种中，它们的羽毛被磨損，变为[[赭色|赭色]]。体型较大的[[雄性|雄性]]平均体重为4.57[[千克|千克]]，而[[雌性|雌性]]的平均体重为4.02千克。所有亚种的平均体重在2.7-6.7千克之间。<ref>[http://bna.birds.cornell.edu/bna/species/031/galleries/data/app2/ Sandhill Crane. Appendix 2] {{Wayback|url=http://bna.birds.cornell.edu/bna/species/031/galleries/data/app2/ |date=20160829222319 }}. The Birds of North America. bna.birds.cornell.edu</ref>
<ref name = "CRC">''CRC Handbook of Avian Body Masses'', John B. Dunning, Jr. (ed.). CRC Press (1992), {{ISBN|978-0-8493-4258-5}}.</ref>沙丘鹤的前额为红色，脸颊为白色，拥有长而黑的尖[[鳥喙|喙]]。在飞行时，他它们长而黑的双腿摆在后面，颈部和脖子保持伸直状态。幼鸟身体上部呈红棕色，下部呈灰色。<ref>[http://www.allaboutbirds.org/guide/Sandhill_Crane/id Sandhill Crane] {{Wayback|url=http://www.allaboutbirds.org/guide/Sandhill_Crane/id |date=20181125162838 }}. Allaboutbirds.org. Retrieved on 2012-12-30.</ref><ref>[http://www.seattleaudubon.org/birdweb/bird_details.aspx?id=132 Sandhill Crane] {{Wayback|url=http://www.seattleaudubon.org/birdweb/bird_details.aspx?id=132 |date=20110719080955 }}. Seattleaudubon.org. Retrieved on 2012-12-30.</ref>不同亚种的体型差异很大；它们的平均高度在80-122厘米之间。<ref>[http://www.savingcranes.org/sandhill-crane.html Sandhill Crane] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121013152216/http://www.savingcranes.org/sandhill-crane.html |date=13 October 2012 }}, International Crane Foundation</ref><ref name= NatGeo>Dunn, J.L. & Alderfer, J., editors. Field Guide to the Birds of North America. National Geographic, Washington, D.C.</ref>它们的[[翼弦|翼弦]]长度在42-60[[厘米|厘米]]之间，尾部长度在10-26厘米之间，暴露[[鳥喙|喙]]峰长6.9-16厘米，[[跗骨|跗骨]]长15.5 -26.6厘米。<ref>Johnsgard, Paul A. (1983). [http://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1025&context=bioscicranes Cranes of the World: Sandhill Crane (''Grus canadensis'')] {{Wayback|url=http://digitalcommons.unl.edu/cgi/viewcontent.cgi?article=1025&context=bioscicranes |date=20200113222010 }}. University of Nebraska-Lincoln</ref>

成年沙丘鹤的翼展在1.65至2.30米之间，大型的双翼有利于它们更好的飞翔，与[[鹰|鹰]]和[[鵰|鵰]]的风格类似。<ref name= NatGeo/>它們利用上升的暖气流获得升力，可以在空中飞行数小时而不停歇。

==分类学==
在之前的分类中，沙丘鹤属于[[鹤属|鹤属]]。但2010年发表的一项[[分子系统发生学|分子系统发生学]]研究表明，鹤属是[[多系群|多系群]]的。<ref>{{cite journal | last1=Krajewski | first1=C. | last2=Sipiorski | first2=J.T. | last3=Anderson | first3=F.E. | year=2010 | title=Mitochondrial genome sequences and the phylogeny of cranes (Gruiformes:  Gruidae) | journal=Auk | volume=127 | issue=2 | pages=440–452 | doi=10.1525/auk.2009.09045 | url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/277486138_Complete_Mitochondrial_Genome_Sequences_and_the_Phylogeny_of_Cranes_Gruiformes_Gruidae | access-date=2018-11-25 | archive-date=2019-05-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190519055349/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/277486138_Complete_Mitochondrial_Genome_Sequences_and_the_Phylogeny_of_Cranes_Gruiformes_Gruidae | dead-url=no }}</ref>所以，在之后对鹤科重新分类中，沙丘鹤、[[白枕鹤|白枕鹤]]、[[赤颈鹤|赤颈鹤]]和[[澳洲鹤|澳洲鹤]]被移到了[[赤颈鹤属|赤颈鹤属]]。赤颈鹤属这一分类最早由[[德国|德国]]鸟类学家[[路德維希·賴興巴赫|路德維希·賴興巴赫]]于1853年提出。<ref name=ioc>{{cite web | editor1-last=Gill | editor1-first=Frank | editor2-last=Donsker | editor2-first=David | year=2017 | title=Rails, gallinules, trumpeters & cranes | work=World Bird List Version 7.2 | url=http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/rails/ | publisher=International Ornithologists' Union | accessdate=2017-06-28 | archive-date=2018-08-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180825000722/http://www.worldbirdnames.org/bow/rails/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book | last=Reichenbach | first=Ludwig | author-link=路德維希·賴興巴赫 | year=1853 | title=Reichenbach Handbuch der speciellen Ornithologie | publisher=Friedrich Hofmeister | place=Leipzig | page=xxiii | url=https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47618653 | access-date=2018-11-25 | archive-date=2018-12-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181201135438/https://www.biodiversitylibrary.org/page/47618653 | dead-url=no }}</ref>

